  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dc3\u0dca\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dbb \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dca\u0da8\u0dcf\u0dc3 7 \u0d9a\u0da7 \u0d87\u0db3\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd3\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba \u0db4\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Curfew is imposed on 7 western police divisions",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Inspector General of Police C. said that police curfew has been imposed from 9.00 pm today (8) until further notice, covering all the police areas of 7 police divisions in the Western Province. D. Mr. Wickramaratne announced.",
        "Police curfew has been imposed in Negombo, Kelaniya, Nugegoda, Mt. Colombo (North), Colombo (South) and Colombo (Central) Divisions and all people in those police areas should stay in their homes while violating the police curfew is disturbing to maintain public order. The announcement of the Inspector General states that the law will be strictly enforced.",
        "The Inspector General of Police further said in the announcement that traveling through the areas where police curfew is in effect is completely prohibited and for that other alternative routes should be used."
      ],
